{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take a relaxing walk around a surprise-filled island and build your own secret base! Explore the island, meet cute animals, play fun mini-games, and collect cool toys and furniture. Enjoy carefree and happy moments on the island! Play with your friends and share the fun together! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wander around the island: Roam aimlessly across the island, go wherever you want, and explore to your heart's content!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plant various vegetables: Grow vegetables, earn coins, and use them to unlock surprises from the gacha machine!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect fun toys: Discover and collect many unique toys scattered around the island!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet cute animals: Find and bring home adorable animals that you encounter in different places on the island!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create your own secret base: Use the toys and furniture you collect to decorate and create your own secret base!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with friends: The game supports multiplayer, so enjoy the fun times with your friends!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the relaxing island life: Bask in the carefree moments on the island, relax, and enjoy every second!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.aka